<!--
  A tick with stroke contrast: thin on the way down, heavy on the way up. Drawn, not iconised — a
  uniform check is the single most templated mark a todo app can have. The dot is the full stop in
  "Listo.", sitting on the tick's baseline; it ties the wordmark to the mark.
  108x108 adaptive viewport; everything sits inside the 66dp safe circle.
-->
